{"tid":1855954,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家清醒啲望清楚現實","createTime":"2020-02-01T10:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T11:08:53.000Z","uid":28970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8da8108fcf7648ddbf93b3aefe90f676bbf616d","tid":1855954,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"頭先屋企2件廢人話罷工on9醫者父母心<br />\n應該換撚走曬用支那醫生<br />\n<br />\n大家要將藍絲同支那豬睇齊唔好因為咁而掉以輕心<br />\n依2種人嘅奴性已經入撚左血只會見到棺材先知奶野<br />\n<br />\n抗疫抗爭係2件事支那人同藍絲唔值得我地可憐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>講白啲就係仲有好撚多蠢閪比依啲虛偽呃到</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清算藍絲敵視支那人不分化不篤灰不割席依幾個宗旨係核心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，用緊潛行mode喺各大藍血谷嘅手足留意如果覺得自己思路好亂要停一停，調整好先再用過潛行mode <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我準備好同醫護一齊罷！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfRX2Or.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfRX2Or.gif&h=b91bea34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1edb6819f87ace777c9fd9dcb282f8c8fac3b49","tid":1855954,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"政府一日唔全面封關，只會鼓勵更多疫區感染者衝入香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死更多人，<span style=\"color: gold;\">現全體香港市民要求將所有口岸（包括機場、羅湖、落馬洲、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋）全面禁止來自中國大陸旅客入境香港，否則繼續三罷！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">備注：<br />\n1.）非中國大陸旅客（包括台灣）可以正常入境香港<br />\n2.）擁有香港永久性居民身分可以正常入境香港<br />\n3.）任何人經中國大陸入境香港必須接受為期14日隔離及醫學監察</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">工欲善其事必先利其器，你又入咗工會未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ile0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=4b8a8642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️Group List⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike/1040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F1040&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ile0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=4211468c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike/1040</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ile0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=03bd07c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ile0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=844fe3a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"http://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ile0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=dbc03333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/33hmGRR</a></span>"},{"pid":"6c65810f288df83eb7d182dd70567d3c47f3cc3c","tid":1855954,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"屋企兩件廢老同你果個一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2131ddf52e6689a7b4b369a4a0c1e7d0a6dfd3d","tid":1855954,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c65810f288df83eb7d182dd70567d3c47f3cc3c","tid":1855954,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"屋企兩件廢老同你果個一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}